name: Monster Food #1
description:
Monster Food Art (for their acronym MFA), is an agency in charge of protecting humanity from extinction, nowadays facing mutant food, influenced by a pathogen, out of public knowledge.

For the moment, the MFA has studied fifty creatures, which have been stuffed and are for sale, being part of the first Monster Food Art collection. 

Subsequently will come more, thanks to technological advances, that the agency pretends to achieve in the future not so far.
